## Frontend environment overrides (Vite)
#
# By default, the frontend will connect to the backend using:
# - the same hostname as the current page
# - port 5000
#
# If your backend runs elsewhere, set these in `autofe-frontend/.env`:
#
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://127.0.0.1:5000
# VITE_WS_URL=http://127.0.0.1:5000
#
# Notes:
# - `VITE_WS_URL` is a Socket.IO endpoint (HTTP/HTTPS). Socket.IO upgrades to WebSocket internally.
# - `ws://` / `wss://` will also work (auto-normalized), but `http(s)` is recommended.

